{"title_page": "REICK (DJ)", "text_new": "'''[Koushik Mukherjee]''' known professionally as '''[REICK]''' ''(previously went by the stage name Koushik Mukherjee)'' is an [[Indian people|Indian]] [[Disc jockey|DJ]], songwriter and record producer based in [[Kolkata]], [[India]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/artist/koushik-mukherjee-mn0003582679/discography|title=Koushik Mukherjee {{!}} Album Discography|website=AllMusic|language=en-us|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/4DPP90htu1QIrbeZ6g3OAs|title=REICK|website=Spotify|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>  \n\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| background       = non_vocal_instrumentalist\n| image            = Reickshoot1.jpg\n| alias            = Koushik Mukherjee, DJ Koushik, REICK\n| birth_name       = Koushik Mukherjee\n| birth_place      = kolkata, India\n| caption          = REICK at The Westin Kolkata 2019\n| genre            = {{flatlist|\n* [[Trap music (EDM)|Trap]]\n* [[Electronic dance music|EDM]]\n* [[tropical house]] \n* [[French house]]\n* [[moombahton]]\n* [[dubstep]]\n* [[pop music|pop]]\n* [[Hip hop music|hip hop]]\n* [[House music|bass house]]\n}}\n| instrument       = {{flatlist|\n* Keyboards\n* piano\n* [[synthesizer]]\n}}\n| name             = REICK\n| occupation       = {{flatlist|\n* DJ\n* record producer\n}}\n| origin           = [[Kolkata]], India\n| years_active     = 2009\u2013present\n}}\n\nHe is best known for his ability to create an unique vibe while performing or producing music. Some of his most popular tracks are \"'''Slow Love'''\" featuring [[Jimmy Burney]] , \"'''There For You'''\" which did turn out to be an important mark to begin his career as a record producer.\n\n== Career ==\n'''REICK''' has performed across the country at various clubs, music festivals alongside some of the finest Indian and international artists.\n\nHe has began his career interning with [[The Thrillseekers]] which did help him gain interest and perfect his art for electronic music.\n\nHe made his first official release '''\"There For You\"''' as Koushik Mukherjee which peaked onto #52 rank on Top 100 Electronica charts at [[Beatport]]. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/there-for-you-mw0003010771|title=There for You - Koushik Mukherjee {{!}} Songs, Reviews, Credits|website=AllMusic|language=en-us|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.beatport.com/artist/koushik-mukherjee/580276|title=Koushik Mukherjee Tracks & Releases on Beatport|website=www.beatport.com|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n\nSuccess came in as he dropped his new single '''[https://fanlink.to/reickmusic \"Slow Love\"]''' under his new stage name '''REICK'''. Slow Love garnered a lot of attention with it peaking onto #2 rank on [[ITunes Store|iTunes]] India Dance Charts and #91 on iTunes India charts <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kworb.net/itunes/artist/reick.html|title=REICK Chart Positions on iTunes/Spotify/YouTube|website=kworb.net|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref> within the first week of the release. Slow Love has over 1.1 Million views on [[YouTube (channel)|YouTube]]<ref>{{Citation|title=REICK ft. Jimmy Burney - Slow Love (Official Music Video)|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9hqVWE8QEA0|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref> , and is also being aired on [[VH1 India|Vh1]].\n\n== Discography ==\n\n=== '''Singles''' ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Title             \n!Year\n!Album\n!Notes\n|-\n|\"Himalaya\" \ncredited as a co producer\n\nfo inDjnous Tribe along with Dj Harish <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.beatport.com/track/himalaya-original-mix/4211508|title=Himalaya (Original Mix) by DJ Harish, Sid & Koushik, InDJnous Tribe on Beatport|website=www.beatport.com|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>    \n|2013  \n|Single \n|\n|-\n|\"There For You\"\ncredited as Koushik Mukherjee <ref>{{Citation|title=\u200eThere For You - Single by Koushik Mukherjee|url=https://music.apple.com/in/album/there-for-you-single/1161489482|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=There For You|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/0mArWEN2kSjLh5hrlCO96Q|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Koushik-Mukherjee-There-For-You/release/9436847|title=Koushik Mukherjee - There For You|website=Discogs|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|2016\n|Single  \n|Ranked #52 on Beaport Top 100 Electronica Charts\n|-\n|\"Slow Love\" feat. [[Jimmy Burney]] \ncredited as REICK <ref>{{Citation|title=Slow Love|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/6i2Zclop35JchX5Z83CVGi|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/in/artist/reick/1479322253|title=\u200eREICK on Apple Music|website=Apple Music|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://testicanzoni.mtv.it/testi-REICK_40242992/testo-Slow-Love-(Radio-Edit)-%5Bfeat.-Jimmy-Burney%5D-100393547|title=Slow Love (Radio Edit) [feat. Jimmy Burney] (Testo) - REICK|website=MTV Testi e Canzoni|language=it|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n|2019\n|Single\n|Ranked #2 on iTunes India (Dance Charts)\nRanked #91 on iTunes India Charts\n\n1.1+ Million Views on YouTube\n\nAiring on Vh1\n|}\n\n== Further reading ==\n\n* Coverage by [[The Telegraph (Kolkata)|The Telegraph]] <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/entertainment/winter-party-in-association-with-t2/cid/1414168|title=Winter Party in association with t2|website=www.telegraphindia.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/culture/t2-turned-11-this-year-and-we-dedicated-the-special-moment-to-you-mdash-the-t2-reader/cid/1383553|title=t2 turned 11 this year, and we dedicated the special moment to you \u2014 the t2 reader!|website=www.telegraphindia.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref>\n*Lyrics of [https://www.metrolyrics.com/slow-love-lyrics-reick.html Slow Love]\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}  <!--- T